# Standard NativeUi lower/serve pipeline

[serve](std/ui/primitives.ssc)
[vstack](std/ui/layout.ssc)
[text, heading](std/ui/typography.ssc)
[styled](std/ui/display.ssc)
[TkNode](std/ui/nodes.ssc)
[lower](std/ui/lower.ssc)
[defaultTheme](std/ui/theme.ssc)

```scalascript
def view(): TkNode =
  vstack(gap = 4)(
    styled(["paddingX" -> "md"])(text("token spacing")),
    styled(["paddingX" -> "12"])(heading(2, "numeric spacing"))
  )

def run(): Unit = serve(lower(view(), defaultTheme), 0)
```
